(2) The Controller or any officer may, at all reasonable times, inspect the book referred to in paragraph (a) of sub-section (1) and make extracts therefrom, and the proper officer shall, on being required to do so by the Controller , or an officer , produce such book for inspection. [As amended by No. 25 of 1969]
